==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Langya
<hw>Lan"gya</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<ety>[Native name Anglicized.]</ety> <def>One of several species of East
Indian and Asiatic fresh-water fishes of the genus
<gen>Ophiocephalus</gen>, remarkable for their power of living out of
water, and for their tenacity of life; -- called also <altname>walking
fishes</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Laniard</ent>⟦br⟧
